mistral.reason: Andy Deemer wrote and directed Poultrygeist: Night of the Chicken Dead, but he did not produce it. He served as a producer for Lloyd Kaufman's film in another context.

gemma2.reason: Several pieces of text directly state that Lloyd Kaufman directed and produced Poultrygeist, and Andy Deemer was a producer on the film, not the director.
